86
00:07:06,855 --> 00:07:08,483
'Cause we broke up.

87
00:07:09,221 --> 00:07:10,435
For real.

88
00:07:12,628 --> 00:07:13,778
It's over.

89
00:07:16,227 --> 00:07:19,048
