175
00:12:56,327 --> 00:12:59,699
So, I'm off duty today,
but here are those marina reports.

176
00:12:59,784 --> 00:13:03,267
And after my workout, I'll swing by
and pick up a copy of the manifesto.

177
00:13:04,872 --> 00:13:06,592
Look at that board.

178
00:13:07,699 --> 00:13:09,567
These kills are precise,

179
00:13:10,253 --> 00:13:13,702
but there's also a fluidity,
even some improvisation.

180
00:13:14,928 --> 00:13:17,278
If I could just find the music...

181
00:13:18,608 --> 00:13:20,493
Want to borrow my Ipod ?

182
00:13:22,588 --> 00:13:24,038
Got any Chopin ?

183
00:13:25,079 --> 00:13:27,474
No. Fresh out of Chopin.

184
00:13:28,290 --> 00:13:29,490
Shit.

185
00:13:29,722 --> 00:13:31,351
Chopin's perfect.

186
00:13:31,627 --> 00:13:33,172
Did you just swear ?

187
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:36,508
What can I say ?
You're rubbing off on me, Morgan.

188
00:13:37,828 --> 00:13:39,698
But Chopin is perfect.

189
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:43,949
So this is how you do what you do.

190
00:13:47,384 --> 00:13:50,631
The truth speaks to me
from a peaceful place.

191
00:13:51,827 --> 00:13:53,837
I got to set the stage to hear it.

192
00:13:53,858 --> 00:13:55,361
You know what I mean ?

193
00:13:58,728 --> 00:14:00,278
I thrive on chaos.

194
00:14:08,228 --> 00:14:09,978
But this is good, too.

195
00:14:24,928 --> 00:14:26,478
I didn't kill her.

196
00:14:27,814 --> 00:14:29,895
I was just trying
to stop the blood.

197
00:14:33,315 --> 00:14:35,187
<i>No forceful impact spatter,</i>

198
00:14:35,222 --> 00:14:37,570
<i>he's telling the truth, I can tell.</i>

199
00:14:38,148 --> 00:14:39,519
Palms up, please.

200
00:14:44,028 --> 00:14:46,922
When I found Betsy,
she was still breathing.

201
00:14:47,350 --> 00:14:49,100
I wanted to help her.

202
00:14:51,812 --> 00:14:53,544
You believe me, right ?

203
00:14:53,832 --> 00:14:56,338
I'm just the lab guy,
Mr. Wilson. Sorry.

204
00:14:58,027 --> 00:15:00,092
Arms down at your sides, please.

205
00:15:04,028 --> 00:15:05,678
<i>Blood misting.</i>

206
00:15:10,428 --> 00:15:13,178
