for evidence.

207
00:15:24,303 --> 00:15:27,494
The girl's mother was at work but she
isn't really defending her husband.

208
00:15:27,827 --> 00:15:30,314
Wilson and his stepdaughter
fought all the time.

209
00:15:30,351 --> 00:15:32,825
