no doubt about it.

221
00:16:04,127 --> 00:16:08,173
Okay, Morgan. Make sure you get me
your blood report as soon as possible.

222
00:16:15,027 --> 00:16:17,402
<i>This is my chance
to make Doakes go away</i>

223
00:16:17,437 --> 00:16:20,343
<i>without spilling a single drop
of his blood.</i>

224
00:16:20,609 --> 00:16:24,159
