227
00:16:40,858 --> 00:16:42,893
<i>I like the sound of that.</i>

228
00:16:42,928 --> 00:16:46,178
Yeah, I had to do a little
creative problem-solving

229
00:16:46,213 --> 00:16:48,075
at someone else's expense.

230
00:16:48,137 --> 00:16:49,328
<i>Bravo.</i>

231
00:16:49,527 --> 00:16:51,708
<i>Yeah, I figured you'd like that.</i>

232
00:16:51,737 --> 00:16:52,793
<i>What's up ?</i>

233
00:16:52,828 --> 00:16:55,378
Well, you know
that art installation

234
00:16:55,413 --> 00:16:56,917
