235
00:16:57,128 --> 00:16:58,478
The cannibals.

236
00:16:58,628 --> 00:17:02,122
<i>They're not cannibals.
How barbaric !</i>

237
00:17:02,943 --> 00:17:07,379
Their eating is symbolic of the way
we consume others to feed our needs.

238
00:17:07,582 --> 00:17:09,753
<i>- That's what I meant.
- Well...</i>

239
00:17:10,494 --> 00:17:11,835
it sold.

240
00:17:11,849 --> 00:17:14,666
I didn't even create it
to sell, but one of my buyers

241
00:17:14,745 --> 00:17:17,588
<i>fell in love with it,
and I named an outrageous price,</i>

242
00:17:17,623 --> 00:17:20,183
<i>and she paid me a deposit
on the spot.</i>

243
00:17:20,728 --> 00:17:21,928
So...

244
00:17:23,427 --> 00:17:25,446
You in the mood to celebrate ?

245
00:17:33,828 --> 00:17:35,028
Definitely.

