00:51:07,785 --> 00:51:10,921
and they can't hardly even talk
to men until they get married.

742
00:51:19,706 --> 00:51:22,898
The new king, Abdullah,
is trying to change some old bad rules,

743
00:51:22,975 --> 00:51:24,844
so women can do more things...

744
00:51:28,159 --> 00:51:32,796
Thank you very much for listening.
Or, as they say in Arabic, "shokran".

745
00:51:58,477 --> 00:52:00,977
I can't believe how calm
you were up there.

746
00:52:01,012 --> 00:52:03,477
Yeah, you were like
a professional talker.

747
00:52:03,512 --> 00:52:05,190
You were pretty good.

748
00:52:05,872 --> 00:52:08,306
Can Dexter come for ice cream
with us ?

749
00:52:09,710 --> 00:52:11,417
Can he, mom, please ?

750
00:52:13,136 --> 00:52:15,435
- Sure, Dexter can join us.
- I wouldn't miss it.

751
00:52:15,470 --> 00:52:19,094
Maybe they'll have some delicious
Saudi flavors, like sand or oil.

752
00:52:20,878 --> 00:52:22,528
Hang on a sec, guys.

753
00:52:28,318 --> 00:52:29,727
Are you hurt ?

754
00:52:31,073 --> 00:52:32,836
Okay. I'm coming now.

755
00:52:35,616 --> 00:52:37,066
I know. Me too.

756
00:52:42,008 --> 00:52:44,579
Come on, kids.
Dexter won't be joining us.

757
00:52:44,614 --> 00:52:48,058
Rita, it's an emergency.
Look, I'm so sorry, you guys.

758
00:52:48,127 --> 00:52:51,047
I'll make it up to you, but I gotta
help a friend who's in trouble.

759
00:52:51,082 --> 00:52:53,845
There was a fire at her place.
I'm so sorry.

760
00:52:55,719 --> 00:52:57,132
Hey, let's go.

761
00:53:24,979 --> 00:53:26,369
What happened ?

762
00:53:28,368 --> 00:53:30,909
I was working on my piece
with the blowtorch,

763
00:53:30,944 --> 00:53:33,450
and it just caught fire.
I was so scared.

764
00:53:33,485 --> 00:53:34,816
I guess so.

765
00:53:41,074 --> 00:53:43,585
Promise me that you won't leave me,

766
00:53:43,620 --> 00:53:45,647
that you won't go anywhere.

767
00:53:46,467 --> 00:53:48,352
I'm not going anywhere.

768
00:53:59,930 --> 00:54:02,156
Hey, you got your light fixed.

